name: Heal You - Fitness App UI Kit
description: Hello Everyone. Meet Heal You, it is a premium UI Kit consist of 80+ health & fitness app screens that can help you to boost your design process. This kit is carefully crafted and contains many UI components that you can use for design inspiration or speed up your design workflow. You can also find a series of screens that guide users through the app interface & functions. You can make your custom workout on this app. You can track your daily activity & set up an alarm for your exercise time. Easy to customize to fit your style. Also, You can get a dark mode version of it.
